<p><b>What is the just a minute strategy?</b> Just a Minute game is a simple game but effective to improve students' speaking skill. The rule of the game is the students speak in one minute about a topic given by teacher without hesitation, repetition, and deviation. If the students break the rule, the other students can take the chance by saying “Challenge”.</p>
